{"tid":2261091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時真係逼於無奈要搭黨鐵","createTime":"2020-10-28T05:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T06:02:42.000Z","uid":312542,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc879bd7ceed26a609e8ef4b6539b3075fb799ea","tid":2261091,"uid":312542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"人生總有啲時候係避免唔到要搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如同同事出去見客<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又例如趕時間時撞正繁忙時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近搭得密咗...然後身邊有朋友話想買番張綠卡<br />\n我開始疑惑應該用咩心態去搭黨鐵同用綠卡<br />\n<br />\n想問大家一個問題：<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"large\">今時今日，究竟拍邊張卡先合乎道義？<br />\n</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：成人/學生 &lt;- 一係唔搭，搭就跟番規矩！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：綠卡 &lt;- 係黨鐵得罪香港人在先，而家洗咩尊重佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係諗唔通...<br />\n所以都係多啲提醒自己，罷到鐵就罷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">831打死人</span></span>"},{"pid":"e10f5a52553eaaa45ee80f1b181fcc8ced9b676b","tid":2261091,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"乜都好 量力而為"},{"pid":"0a6ab9594ad4f64a9552ae9c9638901b0b6604b6","tid":2261091,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"做人洗咩講咁多黃藍<br />\n不過你要用佢服務就守規矩俾正價<br />\n呢一樣係公民意識同法律"},{"pid":"2634bd3eeb3f6bcc5586f32cccb9e8795cbdf18b","tid":2261091,"uid":258631,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"早啲出發唔得嘅？"},{"pid":"50242280c50e491fe9f60fa6e72b6b6880110d1a","tid":2261091,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2634bd3eeb3f6bcc5586f32cccb9e8795cbdf18b","tid":2261091,"uid":258631,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"re